From 65497974ad95b0f3d193637aa646ed8e6b9290fd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SlayZone Dev <dev@slayzone.local>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 21:21:21 +0200
Subject: [slayzone] slayzone: Phase 8.3 test webui + SlayzoneTestHost

Third Phase 8 home-panel port. Read-only in 8.3; rescan RPC + settings
dialog wire up in Phase 8.5 / Phase 10. Labels + notes + tree grouping
are deferred to Phase 17 polish.

- chrome/browser/slayzone/mojom/test.mojom: TestHost with
  GetSnapshot() => (TestSnapshot). TestFile carries path, category,
  status, durationMs; TestCategory is a name + count header.
- slayzone_test_host.{h,cc}: per-SlayzoneBrowserView Mojo impl.
  GetSnapshot forwards to SidecarClient::Call(test:get-snapshot).
- slayzone_test_ui.{h,cc}: chrome://slayzone-test/ WebUIController
  using slayzone::ConfigureBundleSource helper.
- SlayzoneBrowserView: owns a SlayzoneTestHost + test_host() accessor.
- ChromeURLHosts() + webui_url_constants + registry + binder updated.
- BUILD.gn: new .cc/.h files wired into browser + ui targets;
  mojom/BUILD.gn adds test.mojom.
